**Parking Birmingham dataset**

The data was collected from car parks in Birmingham that are operated by NCP from Birmingham City Council. It contains the occupancy rates (8:00 to 16:30) from 2016/10/04 to 2016/12/19.

### Attribute information

- SystemCodeNumber: Car park ID 
- Capacity: Car park capacity 
- Occupancy: Car park occupancy rate 
- LastUpdated: Date and Time of the measure
